<p><strong>Keep it Short.</strong> If you can keep an email to less than 2 or 3 sentences, itâ€™s much easier to read it right then. If your email is longer than a paragraph or two, people will often put off reading it and it will probably take you longer to get a response.</p>

<p>Bad:</p>

